ookbook Launch - Build Secure AI Apps in Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#privateindependentllmdevelopmentwithollamaandpython-breakfreeofpublicmodelrestraints"&gt;Private, Independent LLM Development with Ollama and Python - Break Free of Public Model Restraints&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildaiandllmappswithlangchainin2plushourswithpython"&gt;Build AI and LLM Apps with LangChain in 2+ HOURS with Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildgenaiwithtransformernlpdeeplearningtensorflowkerasandpython"&gt;Build GenAI with Transformer NLP Deep Learning, TensorFlow Keras and Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#aiappdevelopmentmastery-buildvideovisionandwhisperpythonprojects"&gt;AI App Development Mastery - Build Video, Vision and Whisper Python Projects&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#datatrainingmasterclass-humansupervisionmachinelearningwithpython"&gt;Data Training Masterclass - Human Supervision Machine Learning with Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#thecompletepythonalgorithmsbundledebut"&gt;The Complete Python Algorithms Bundle Debut&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#generativedeeplearningfromscratch-buildneuralnetworksin5plushourswithpython"&gt;Generative Deep Learning from Scratch - Build Neural Networks in 5+ HOURS with Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#5plushourhands-onaiengineering-buildappswithfoundationmodelsinpython"&gt;5+ HOUR Hands-On AI Engineering - Build Apps with Foundation Models in Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#llmlanguageunderstandingandgenerationinpython"&gt;LLM Language Understanding and Generation in Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#crackthemachinelearninginterviewwith6-figuresalaryquestions"&gt;Crack the Machine Learning Interview with 6-Figure Salary Questions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#thecomplete5plushourpythondeeplearningforstocksbundle"&gt;The Complete 5+ HOUR Python Deep Learning for Stocks Bundle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#promptengineeringartandscience-buildllm-basedappsinpython"&gt;Prompt Engineering Art and Science - Build LLM-Based Apps in Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#thecompleteappdevelopmentwithgpt-4inpythonmasterclass"&gt;The Complete App Development with GPT-4 in Python Masterclass&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#best-sellingmicrosoftcopilotinexcel-promptengineeringtoolkit"&gt;Best-Selling Microsoft CoPilot in Excel - Prompt Engineering Toolkit&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#promptengineeringperfectionplaybookforgenerativeaiwithpython"&gt;Prompt Engineering Perfection Playbook for Generative AI with Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#5plushourgenaiappdevelopmentwithgooglegeminiinpythonunreal5godotandunity"&gt;5+ HOUR GenAI App Development with Google Gemini in Python, Unreal 5, Godot &amp; Unity&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildcomputervisionprojectswithneuralnetworkstesseractandopencvinpython"&gt;Build Computer Vision Projects with Neural Networks, Tesseract and OpenCV in Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#naturallanguageprocessingmachinelearningbootcampwithpython"&gt;Natural Language Processing Machine Learning Bootcamp with Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#algorithmictradingwithnaturallanguageprocessingandmachinelearninginpython"&gt;Algorithmic Trading with Natural Language Processing and Machine Learning in Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#theessentialcopilotpromptengineeringcookbook"&gt;The Essential Copilot Prompt Engineering Cookbook&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#1rankedpythonmachinelearning6plushourbundlewithcursor-masterai-poweredcoding"&gt;#1 Ranked Python Machine Learning 6+ HOUR Bundle with Cursor - Master AI-Powered Coding&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildviralgenerativeaiappswithgptinpython"&gt;Build Viral Generative AI Apps with GPT in Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#1googlegeminichatbotpromptengineering4plushourbundle"&gt;#1 Google Gemini Chatbot Prompt Engineering 4+ HOUR Bundle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#essentialanthropicpromptengineeringmastery5plushourbundle"&gt;Essential Anthropic Prompt Engineering Mastery 5+ HOUR Bundle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#financemachinelearning3plushourbundlewithpythonandcursorai"&gt;Finance Machine Learning 3+ HOUR Bundle with Python and Cursor AI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#designllmapps-acompleteapproachinpython"&gt;Design LLM Apps - A Complete Approach in Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildrecommendationalgorithms-machinelearningtotriggerclicksinpython"&gt;Build Recommendation Algorithms - Machine Learning to Trigger Clicks in Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="dataengineerportfolioreadiness-pythonandpandasexplorationandmanipulationprojects"&gt;&lt;a id="dataengineerportfolioreadiness-pythonandpandasexplorationandmanipulationprojects"&gt;Data Engineer Portfolio Readiness - Python and Pandas Exploration and Manipulation Projects&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/2ee6fbcbe013a453b84e36b3dabf13ac14d4c650.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=bd9408c426398ceb374155d4c267a042"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ready to land your next role in data engineering? This hands-on course helps you build a job-ready portfolio by mastering Python and Pandas—the essential toolkit for every modern data engineer.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;✅ Work with real-world datasets to perform in-depth data exploration and cleaning&lt;br&gt;✅ Use Pandas for filtering, grouping, reshaping, merging, and advanced transformation tasks&lt;br&gt;✅ Visualize and summarize large datasets to prepare for pipelines and modeling&lt;br&gt;✅ Handle missing values, detect outliers, and prepare production-grade data structures&lt;br