;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=87fa66006ee66483dfbdd5dcb75493a0"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This project includes everything pictured, including all assets, maps, and Materials created in the Unreal Engine. Each asset was created for realistic AAA-quality visuals, style, and budget.Technical details&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Throttle can be controlled by W key and S key&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Steer can be controlled by A key and D key&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Camera Rotation can be controlled by Mouse&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Materials are changeable in Detail Panel&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Setup for easy drop and play&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Custom sounds&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Master Material to control features&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Multiple Design Skins&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Includes Static Mesh Version&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;2K and 4K Texture Sets&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Master material setup that control shader looks&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Additional controls for roughness, albedo, normals and more&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Channel packed Roughness | Metalness | Ambient Occlusion&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Optimized for games&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Free of all legal issues as all branding and labels are custom made by our studio&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Fully detailed models from all sides&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Includes test dynamic lighting scene&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Blueprints: 1&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Input: See above&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Network Replicated: No&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: All&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Windows: Yes&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Mac: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxcyberpunk"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxcyberpunk" href="https://youtu.be/K1bhBMdqWq0"&gt;SFX Cyberpunk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/54d5293ed9ca7376c5cb1fd91cc39acea90b0c44.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=75b889d5b7aeec7511da305f0e5a7546"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A futuristic sound pack tailored for cyberpunk environments. Includes ambient loops, electrical malfunctions, ventilator hums, and rainy dystopian city textures—perfect for sci-fi worlds, hacking sequences, or neon-lit streets.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="zbrush_beginnertoadvancedcourseonthreeminiatures"&gt;&lt;a id="zbrush_beginnertoadvancedcourseonthreeminiatures" href="https://youtu.be/F_9JzAHvNKM"&gt;ZBrush: Beginner to Advanced Course on Three Miniatures&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Step into the world of ZBrush as you embark on a journey to craft three miniature figures . Our Udemy course is your ticket to mastering the sculpting, material, and landscapes. Our instructor from Brazil, Celito Moura, has been working in the cinema industry since 2003 as a 3D artist, concept artist, storyboardist, texture artist, and art director. His clientele includes Cartoon Network, Napster, Banco do Brasil, and many others. Currently he is focused on the area of miniatures and collectibles. With his experience, this course is tailored for from beginners and experienced artists. You’ll start by gaining a solid foundation in the principles of sculpting, clothing and anatomy. Throughout the course, you’ll engage in a practical project designed to sharpen your skills and deepen your understanding of the creative process. By the end, you’ll emerge with a portfolio-worthy environment, ready to showcase your talent and impress potential employers. Key topics include: Understanding the principles of sculpting Navigating ZBrush’s robust toolset and features Using and creating brushes Posing, finalizing, and optimizing your models for rendering Exporting your miniature for production Taking renders on Blender and Photoshop Whether you’re an enthusiast looking to break into the gaming industry or a professional seeking to refine your craft, this course offers invaluable insights and practical skills to elevate your character art.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vfxsmokeunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="vfxsmokeunrealengine"&gt;VFX Smoke (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9ace05535f5b6568170dcdd06b51e66c3bc5d8ca.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=b228981cc74b69570e508f54a2b171bf"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A realistic smoke VFX pack featuring dense fog, chimney smoke, and toxic emission effects. Perfect for environmental storytelling, industrial scenes, and atmospheric layering in Unreal Engine projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="watervfxunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="watervfxunrealengine"&gt;Water VFX (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e7e0a696568a7ec07a7a8b3bace46347c5706831.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ab4a30091a8be98f1f99265df6742a55"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Leartes Presents Awesome VFX Pack:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Unreal Engine Version: 5.0&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The Water VFX Packs include:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Heavy Rain&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Light Rain&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Snow&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Water Dripple&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Waterfall&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Water Flow&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Water fountain&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Water Leak&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="objectdistributiontoolunrealenginetoolplugin"&gt;&lt;a id="objectdistributiontoolunrealenginetoolplugin" href="https://youtu.be/qWYrB-D7W1g"&gt;Object Distribution Tool (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/07173d4d7724dfb57cdf15d95bbfff96e5ed8e40.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=0f4397b150d22f00785a74fdf3f940c6"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Welcome to the innovative world of Leartes Studios, where passion for gaming meets Unreal Engine’s automation possibilities. Leartes Studios is dedicated to pushing the boundaries of being a leading art outsourcing company.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Quick access to the tool interface with a custom tool menu&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;The customizable window for personal uses&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Allows you to automatically create a preset from the selected assets in the Content Browser.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;A new parameter called ""Spawn Density"" has been added, which allows bulk adjustment of object counts quantities in a specified proportion, enabling easy increase or decrease of object placements.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;No custom class dependencies can be removed from the project at any time&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create and simulate an unlimited number of different mesh types in various arrangements.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Save and reuse builds you created using presets&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Combine your presets with Mixer to instantly create more complex structures.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Code Modules ObjectDistribution(Editor)&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;ObjectDistributionManger(Editor)&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number Of C++ Classes: 21&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Blueprints: 1&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Network Replicated: No&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: Win64&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Supported Target Build Platforms: Win64&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="500plusfantasyiconsunity"&gt;&lt;a id="500plusfantasyiconsunity"&gt;500+ Fantasy Icons&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/2a48efa76b2762883b425eaba75028432715aa29.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=6c32c834ea4f50953032e5a1a96223cb"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Fantasy RPG Icons (500+)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This pack includes highly detailed icons that will be useful for those who create RPG games.FULL PACK CONTENT:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Background and No Background version for ALL Icons!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each icon is 1080x1080 pixels (PNG)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Weapons:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;44x Axes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;40x Daggers&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;47x Shields&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;39x Swords&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Clothings:&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;35x Armors&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;31x Boots&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;28x Helmets&lt;/li&gt;&